The greatest number which will divide 116, 221, 356 leaving the same remainder in each case is? </br> वह संख्या ज्ञात करो, जिसे 116, 221, 356 से विभाजित करने पर समान शेषफल आये?@15@10@5@20@1@‘r’  => 221 – r, 116 – r, 356 – r  </br> [(221 – r) – (116 – r)], [(356 – r) – (116 – r)]. and [(356 – r) – (221 – r)]</br> 105, 135, 240 are divisible by that number </br> = HCF of 105, 135, 140 = 15.